org.apache.poi.hssf.usermodel

Class HSSFShapeGroup

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hssf.usermodel.HSSFShape
      • org.apache.poi.hssf.usermodel.HSSFShapeGroup
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<HSSFShape>, HSSFShapeContainer, Shape, ShapeContainer<HSSFShape> 

    public class HSSFShapeGroup
extends HSSFShape
implements HSSFShapeContainer
    A shape group may contain other shapes. It was no actual form on the sheet.(形状组可以包含其他形状。这张纸上没有真正的表格。)
